INSERT INTO `wpnm_comments` VALUES (2,77,'Sean OConnell','Sean@bluechisranch.com','','71.76.172.83','2017-11-03 02:25:22','2017-11-03 02:25:22','If he is 52 yrs old. Then he was born in 1965. How could he be contributing to the fund since 1956?',0,'0','Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 7.0; VS995 Build/NRD90M; wv) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0 Chrome/61.0.3163.98 Mobile Safari/537.36 [FB_IAB/FB4A;FBAV/147.0.0.44.75;]','',0,0),(3,77,'Melinda Vanatten','vmelinda62@live.com','','174.230.15.180','2017-11-03 13:26:33','2017-11-03 13:26:33','My husband is waiting on a discussion right now.   He was turned down  because lack of medical proof.  He has c.o.p.d, diabetes,  back and hip problems.  Also, he 59 this year.   We are living on my income; get some help from the government.   We had a lawyer,  however they dropped his because,  they felt the case was week.   This was a week before the hearing in front of the Judge.    The discussion we are waiting on is the appeal.   What can we do if he is denied?',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 7.0; SM-G928V Build/NRD90M; wv) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0 Chrome/56.0.2924.87 Mobile Safari/537.36 [FB_IAB/FB4A;FBAV/136.0.0.22.91;]','',0,0),(4,77,'Richard Ketchum','richardketchuh62@hotmail.com','','68.113.176.201','2017-11-18 07:34:07','2017-11-18 07:34:07','had both hips replaced',0,'0','Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 5.1.1; SM-G360V Build/LMY48B) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/61.0.3163.98 Mobile Safari/537.36','',0,0),(5,77,'Glenda leach','fayleach1957@gmail.com','http://fayleach327%20@gmail.com','68.49.46.126','2017-11-18 11:49:41','2017-11-18 11:49:41','I\'m almost 61 and have spinal stenosis I\'ve tryed steroid shots medication physical therapy chiropractic  I have insurance but does not cover surgery my last resort my husband and I are not taking this change in are life\'s very well . my husband is 62 and not healthy he has seizures he reasonally got is disability but its not much 732 a month how we are going to make it is the question I just Stared my disability papers how long will that take?????  To long I know.   Feeling so depressed.  One thing after another now we get a bill in mail for past medical bills over 5000 they can garnish are little amount of money what\'s a person to do pray everyday some thing good to happen',0,'0','Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 6.0.1; 5056N Build/MMB29M; wv) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0 Chrome/62.0.3202.84 Mobile Safari/537.36 [FB_IAB/FB4A;FBAV/150.0.0.38.138;]','',0,0),(6,77,'Claudia Wick','Lynnwick2015@gmailmail.com','','98.29.240.63','2017-11-19 16:45:42','2017-11-19 16:45:42','I got a back pay from Ssi and also ssid and i get ssid but not Ssi  don\'t know why can you help me get my Ssi',0,'0','Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 5.1.1; N9132 Build/LMY47V; wv) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0 Chrome/61.0.3163.98 Mobile Safari/537.36 [FB_IAB/FB4A;FBAV/150.0.0.38.138;]','',0,0),(7,174,'Investigations Toronto','wilhelminaamar@yahoo.com','http://investigationstoronto.com','104.223.29.228','2017-12-04 16:31:07','2017-12-04 16:31:07','Easy to follow, readable...heck I had to leave a commment!',0,'0','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_10_5) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/59.0.3071.115 Safari/537.36','',0,0),(8,174,'Investigations Toronto','aracelywrigley@gmail.com','http://investigationstoronto.com','107.172.128.81','2018-05-18 09:43:54','2018-05-18 09:43:54','Terrific writing on random topics. Im trying to currently \r\n\r\naccomplish something similar to what you have here except \r\nfor on \r\na different topic totally. Many thanks for the inspiration to\r\nwrite better content.',0,'0','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_11_6) AppleWebKit/604.4.7 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/11.0.2 Safari/604.4.7','',0,0),(9,174,'Private Investigator in Mississauga','rosemarieconde@aol.com','http://investigationstoronto.com','146.71.40.215','2018-06-02 23:04:39','2018-06-02 23:04:39','Terrific writing on arbitrary topics. Im trying to currently \r\naccomplish something similar to what you have here except for on \r\na totally different topic. Many thanks for the inspiration to\r\nwrite better content.',0,'0','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_12_6) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/62.0.3202.94 Safari/537.36','',0,0),(10,116,'ergfirnolikz','Forseth77060@gmail.com','http://www.ergfirnolikz.com/','107.178.102.249','2018-07-25 12:26:35','2018-07-25 12:26:35','Great ?V I should definitely pronounce, impressed with your website. I had no trouble navigating through all tabs as well as related information ended up being truly easy to do to access. I recently found what I hoped for before you know it at all. Quite unusual. Is likely to appreciate it for those who add forums or something, site theme . a tones way for your customer to communicate. Nice task..',0,'0','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/62.0.3202.94 Safari/537.36','',0,0);
