mographic that becomes disabled,\" White says. \"This might be a really different cohort of folks that might have a different course of disability than we have seen historically.\"&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;White says if there are resources committed to treatment and to work place accommodations, then a lot of the young people with mental illness should be able to return to full time employment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;new report finds that the number of people who receive Social Security Disability Insurance, or SSDI, due to mental illness has been increasing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Source: &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=\"http://digital.vpr.net/post/number-vermonters-receiving-disability-benefits-due-mental-illness-increasing\"&gt;Number Of Vermonters Receiving Disability Benefits Due To Mental Illness Is Increasing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;__TVE_SHORTCODE_RAW___</div></div>'),(2224,150,'tcb_editor_enabled','1'),(2227,153,'tve_revision_tve_landing_page',''),(2228,153,'tve_revision_tve_content_before_more','<div class=\"thrv_wrapper tve_wp_shortcode\"><div class=\"tve_shortcode_raw\" style=\"display: none\">___TVE_SHORTCODE_RAW__&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=\"http://digital.vpr.net/post/number-vermonters-receiving-disability-benefits-due-mental-illness-increasing#stream/0\"&gt;&lt;img class=\"alignnone size-full\" src=\"https://ssdinsider.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/disability-istock-Hailshadow-20171030-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Originally published by &lt;a href=\"http://digital.vpr.net/post/number-vermonters-receiving-disability-benefits-due-mental-illness-increasing#stream/0\"&gt;Vermont\'s NPR news source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A new&nbsp;&lt;a href=\"http://www.leg.state.vt.us/jfo/issue_briefs_and_memos/SSDI__Mental_Health_and_Musculoskeletal_Diagnoses.pdf\"&gt;report&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;finds that the number of people who receive Social Security Disability Insurance, or SSDI, due to mental illness has been increasing.&lt;/p&gt;