as what Sterling, and the many other disability applicants every year who seek out help, received. Advocacy groups and disability attorneys build sophisticated cases for their clients to ensure that applications make it through all the hoops, and in today’s complex system, it truly takes an expert.</p><p data-css=\"tve-u-15f78183804\">“You can’t do it on your own these days,” Sterling said. “My advocacy group gave me so much help and reassurance. I could have saved myself months of unnecessary anxiety if I had just known that sooner.”<br><br></p></div><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv_heading\"><h1 data-css=\"tve-u-15f7e1d9409\">If You Need Help and Want To Learn More About Advocacy Groups like, <em>Social Security Claim Advocates&nbsp;</em>to See If They Will Take Your Case, Click Below:</h1></div><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv-button\" data-css=\"tve-u-15f7e19144e\">\n<a href=\"http://ssclaimadvocates.com\" class=\"tcb-button-link\" onclick=\"ga(\'send\',\'event\',\'clicks\',\'SSClaim_Advocates_Click\',\'SSDI_Leads\');return\" true;\"\"=\"\" <span=\"\"><span class=\"tcb-button-text thrv-inline-text\">Click Here To Qualify</span>\n</a>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element tve_empty_dropzone\"><p>Or call them directly to have your questions answered even faster: <a href=\"tel:8554820729\">1-855-482-0729</a></p></div><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv-page-section\">\n<div class=\"tve-page-section-out\" data-css=\"tve-u-15f73c2f915\"></div>\n<div class=\"tve-page-section-in tve_empty_dropzone\" data-css=\"tve-u-15f73c2a4e4\"><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element tve_empty_dropzone\" data-css=\"tve-u-15f73c67d17\"><p data-css=\"tve-u-15f73c64b30\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><u>Advertiser Disclosure:&nbsp;&nbsp;</u>SSDInsider is a consumer information site that offers free articles and information relating to Social Security Disability. Many of the companies whose services we mention provide us compensation when someone who clicks from our site becomes their customer. This is how we make money to support our site. Compensation may impact which companies we write about and which articles those companies appear. We do not mention all companies that provide a given service All opinions expressed on this site are our own.</p></div></div>\n</div>'),(4120,264,'tve_revision_tve_content_more_found',''),(4121,264,'tve_revision_tve_save_post',''),(4122,264,'tve_revision_tve_custom_css','@media (min-width: 300px){[data-css=\"tve-u-15f7e19144e\"] { display: block; max-width: 275.333px; }[data-css=\"tve-u-15f7e1d9409\"] { line-height: 1.5em !important; }#tve_editor [data-css=\"tve-u-15f7e1d9409\"] { font-size: 26px !important; }[data-css=\"tve-u-15f7e19144e\"] .tcb-button-link { min-height: 54.7619px; font-size: 1.33333em; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; background-image: none !important; background-color: rgb(31, 84, 145) !important; }[data-css=\"tve-u-15f7cc96c32\"] + div { clear: none; }[data-css=\"tve-u-15f7cc96c32\"] { float: none; width: 768px; }[data-css=\"tve-u-15f781280f9\"] { line-height: 1.25em !important; }#tve_editor [data-css=\"tve-u-15f781280f9\"] { font-size: 2.25em !important; }[data-css=\"tve-u-15f780ffc14\"] { border: none; border-radius: 0px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: -37px !important; margin-right: 0px !important; padding-right: 1px !important; margin-left: 0px !important; padding-left: 1px !important; }[data-css=\"tve-u-15f73d7c1d0\"] { line-height: 35px !important; }#tve_editor [data-css=\"tve-u-15f73d7c1d0\"] { font-size: 1.75em !important; color: rgb(254, 250, 250) !important; }[data-css=\"tve-u-15f73d77486\"] { background-color: rgb(31, 84, 145) !important; }[data-css=\"tve-u-15f73c6a5d7\"] { margin-bottom: -43px !important; }[data-css=\"tve-u-15f73c67d17\"] { margin-top: 58px !important; }#tve_editor [data-css=\"tve-u-15f73c64b30\"] { font-size: 13px !important; }[data-css=\"tve-u-15f73c2f915\"] { background-color: rgb(89, 85, 85) !important; }#tve_editor [data-c