tly reduce the time lost due to technical errors and refiling—one of the top reasons for first-time denials—and greatly improve the chances of a favorable outcome.<br><br>Sterling said he didn’t mind paying after the approval for the immense peace of mind he gained. “Knowing that I had a group of experts fighting for my case meant that I could finally sleep at night.<br><br>I gave myself the best chance of a good outcome.” The best outcome was what Sterling, and the many other disability applicants every year who seek out help, received. <br><br>Advocacy groups and disability attorneys build sophisticated cases for their clients to ensure that applications make it through all the hoops, and in today’s complex system, it truly takes an expert.<br><br>“You can’t do it on your own these days,” Sterling said. “My advocacy group gave me so much help and reassurance. I could have saved myself months of unnecessary anxiety if I had just known that sooner.”</p></div><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv-page-section tcb-window-width\" style=\"width: 892px; left: -116px;\">\n<div class=\"tve-page-section-out\" data-css=\"tve-u-15f73d77486\"></div>\n<div class=\"tve-page-section-in tve_empty_dropzone\" data-css=\"tve-u-15f82cb7092\"><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv_heading\"><h1 data-css=\"tve-u-15f7e1d9409\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Click the button below to receive a free, no obligation consultation with the&nbsp;<em>Social Security Claim Advocates&nbsp;</em>and see if you qualify for them to take your case<a href=\"http://ssclaimadvocates.com\" data-css=\"tve-u-15f82cc5c11\"></a></h1></div></div>\n</div><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv-button\" data-css=\"tve-u-15f82cf36d6\">\n<a href=\"http://ssclaimadvocates.com/\" class=\"tcb-button-link\" onclick=\"ga(\'send\',\'event\',\'clicks\',\'SSClaim_Advocates_Button_Click\',\'SSDI_Leads\');return\" true;\"\"=\"\">\n<span class=\"tcb-button-texts\"><span class=\"tcb-button-text thrv-inline-text\"><u>Click To Qualify</u></span></span>\