et on the phone with an advocacy group right away to see if they could help, it would have saved me months of unnecessary anxiety”.</p><p>To learn more about advocacy groups like the one mentioned in this article, <a href=\"https://www.disability-benefits-help.org/cpc/about-ssdi?utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=cpc&amp;utm_term=disability%20benefits&amp;utm_content=225101598144&amp;utm_campaign=SSD+-+Phrase+Always&amp;__egma[MatchType]=p&amp;__egma[Network]=g&amp;__egma[Device]=c&amp;__egma[Creative]=225101598144&amp;__egma[Placement]=&amp;__egma[AdPosition]=1t1&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMI-_2d2KaM1wIVF7jACh0fsQS1EAAYASAAEgId3_D_BwE\"><u>click here</u></a></p>','DENIED! How 428,654 Disabled Americans Are Using A Little Understood Resource To Finally Get Their Disability Benefits Approved','','inherit','closed','closed','','63-revision-v1','','','2017-10-25 17:32:26','2017-10-25 17:32:26','',63,'https://ssdinsider.com/2017/10/25/63-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(69,1,'2017-10-25 17:36:10','2017-10-25 17:36:10','','DENIED! How 428,654 Disabled Americans Are Using A Little Understood Resource To Finally Get Their Disability Benefits Approved','','inherit','closed','closed','','63-revision-v1','','','2017-10-25 17:36:10','2017-10-25 17:36:10','',63,'https://ssdinsider.com/2017/10/25/63-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(70,1,'2017-10-25 17:37:13','2017-10-25 17:37:13','<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">DENIED! How 428,654 Disabled Americans Are Using A <em>Little Understood</em> Resource To Finally Get Their Disability Benefits Approved.</h1><p>October 27, 2017 Boston, MA:Americans who become disabled and need to apply for Social Security Disability benefits are stunned when they learn how difficult the U.S. Government makes it for them to gain approval.</p><p>John Sterling, a 56-year-old carpenter, became disabled in 2012. “When I got the news from my Doctor that I would not be able to work again, I was struck with a lot of anxiety” John recalls. “A lot of financial worries,