ticated cases for their clients to ensure that applications make it through all the hoops, and in today’s complex system, it truly takes an expert.“You can’t do it on your own these days,” Sterling said. “My advocacy group gave me so much help and reassurance. I could have saved myself months of unnecessary anxiety if I had just known that sooner.”</p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<em>Social Security Claim Advocates&nbsp;</em>does not accept everyone, you must qualify. Get help from the leaders in disability approval today:<a href=\"http://ssclaimadvocates.com\"></a></h1><a href=\"http://ssclaimadvocates.com/\" onclick=\"ga(\'send\',\'event\',\'clicks\',\'SSClaim_Advocates_Button_Click\',\'SSDI_Leads\');return\" true;\"\"=\"\"><span><span><u>Click To Qualify</u></span></span></a><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Or call them directly to have your questions answered even faster:</span><a href=\"tel:8554820729\">1-855-482-0729</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><u>Advertiser Disclosure:&nbsp;&nbsp;</u>SSDInsider is a consumer information site that offers free articles and information relating to Social Security Disability. Many of the companies whose services we mention provide us compensation when someone who clicks from our site becomes their customer. This is how we make money to support our site. Compensation may impact which companies we write about and which articles those companies appear. We do not mention all companies that provide a given service All opinions expressed on this site are our own.</p>','Has This 52 Year Old Disabled American Found The Secret To Disability Benefits Approval?','','inherit','closed','closed','','77-revision-v1','','','2017-11-03 17:24:10','2017-11-03 17:24:10','',77,'https://ssdinsider.com/2017/11/03/77-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(286,1,'2017-11-03 17:25:16','2017-11-03 17:25:16','[tcb-script]fbq(\'track\', \'ViewContent\', {value: 2,currency: \'USD\',});[/tcb-script]<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">Has This 